---
const address = {
  street: 'Avenida del Olivar, 12',
  city: '41940 Sevilla',
  extra: 'Local bajo · Acceso sin escalones',
  mapsQuery: 'Avenida+del+Olivar+12+Sevilla+41940',
};
---

<section class="location" id="ubicacion">
  <div class="location__inner container">
    <header class="location__header">
      <span class="section-label">Dónde estamos</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Ven a vernos</h2>
      <p class="location__intro">Nuestra sede está en Tomares, a un paso de Sevilla. Te esperamos cuando quieras.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="location__body">
      <div class="location__info">
        <div class="location__address">
          <svg class="location__icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M12 2C8.13 2 5 5.13 5 9c0 5.25 7 13 7 13s7-7.75 7-13c0-3.87-3.13-7-7-7z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" fill="none"/>
            <circle cx="12" cy="9" r="2.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" fill="none"/>
          </svg>
          <div>
            <strong>{address.street}</strong><br />
            {address.city}<br />
            <span class="location__extra">{address.extra}</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="location__note">
          ¿Tienes dudas para llegar? Escríbenos y te ayudamos. También realizamos sesiones online para quienes no pueden acercarse presencialmente.
        </p>

        <a
          href={`https://maps.google.com/?q=${address.mapsQuery}`}
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="btn-primary"
        >
          Ver en Google Maps
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="location__map">
        <iframe
          title="Ubicación de MovEmSa en Google Maps"
          src={`https://maps.google.com/maps?q=${address.mapsQuery}&output=embed&z=15`}
          width="100%"
          height="100%"
          loading="lazy"
          referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
          style="border:0;"
          allowfullscreen
        ></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Wave divider -->
  <div class="location__wave" aria-hidden="true">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 1440 80" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" preserveAspectRatio="none">
      <path d="M0,20 C360,70 1080,10 1440,55 L1440,80 L0,80 Z" fill="#E8F6F4"/>
    </svg>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .location {
    position: relative;
    background: var(--clr-bg);
    padding-block: 6rem 9rem;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .location__header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 520px;
    margin-inline: auto;
    margin-block-end: 3.5rem;
  }

  .location__header .section-label {
    display: block;
    margin-block-end: 0.75rem;
  }

  .location__intro {
    margin-block-start: 1rem;
    color: var(--clr-text-muted);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .location__body {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.4fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .location__info {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.75rem;
  }

  .location__address {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--clr-text);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .location__address strong {
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .location__icon {
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-block-start: 0.2rem;
    color: var(--clr-primary-dark);
  }

  .location__extra {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--clr-text-muted);
  }

  .location__note {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--clr-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .location__map {
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    overflow: hidden;
    height: 380px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(22,51,48,0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(75,191,181,0.2);
  }

  .location__map iframe {
    display: block;
  }

  .location__wave {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -1px;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    line-height: 0;
  }

  .location__wave svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 80px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .location__body {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .location__map {
      height: 280px;
    }
  }
</style>
